Every year, Games are held to remember the uprising of District 13, the district that started a fight with the Capitol.
The Capitol answer to that was to hold Games in which a girl and a boy from the ages of 12-18 are chosen to fight. 
There are 2 tributes from all 12 Districts. In District 12, Prim was the girl that was chosen but Katniss who was her sister
decided to volunteer for her. Peeta was the male tribute selected. 